                        <li><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'times new roman', times;">Giá cả hợp lý với hầu bao của khách hàng.</span></li>
                        <li><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'times new roman', times;">Thời gian bảo hành dài hạn cho từng sản phẩm.</span></li>
